dir - request method - parameters - return - explanation

GENERAL
=======
/ - GET - () - (flag:HOME | redirection) - return {"flag": "HOME"} if logged in otherwise redirect to /home
/home - GET - () - (flag:true/false) - return true if logged in otherwise return false

